  "Dear [PG Owner's Name],\n\nWe hope you are doing well. This is to inform you that Kartik and Keshav, tenants of Room No. 8 at Vansh PG, have vacated the room as of 14th June, completing our stay from 15th May to 14th June. We have left the room in the same clean and proper condition as it was when we moved in.\n\nWe would also like to confirm that we have paid the electricity bill in full. The meter reading started at 279 units and ended at 296 units, resulting in a total consumption of:\n\n296 - 279 = 17 units\n17 units × ₹8 = ₹136\n\nSo, we have paid ₹136 towards the electricity charges.\n\nAs our stay has officially ended, we kindly request you not to start the rent for the next month, and you may feel free to allot the room to a new tenant.\n\n\n---\n\nFeedback for Improvement:\n\nWe would also like to share a few suggestions that may help in improving the overall experience for future tenants:\n\n1. Visitors/Friends Policy: Tenants should be allowed to invite their friends without restrictions for casual meetups.\n\n\n2. Freedom for Enjoyment: Light fun and conversations in a louder voice should be allowed, especially during reasonable hours.\n\n\n3. 24×7 Electricity & Wi-Fi: Consistent electricity and internet availability is essential for study and work purposes.\n\n\n4. Water Cooler Safety: The water cooler was giving electric shocks – it needs urgent maintenance for safety.\n\n\n5. Judgemental Environment: Some neighbours seemed to judge us based on dressing sense, which affected our sense of freedom and comfort.\n\n\n6. Air Conditioning: Installing an AC would greatly enhance comfort during peak summer.\n\n\n\nWe hope this feedback will be taken positively and help in improving the PG environment for everyone. Thank you for your support during our stay.\n\nBest regards,\nKartik & Keshav",
  "Hello [PG Owner's Name],\n\nYeh batane ke liye message kar rahe hain ki Room No. 8 (tenants: Kartik aur Keshav) humne 14th June ko vacate kar diya hai. Humne 15th May se 14th June tak yahan stay kiya.\n\nRoom ko waise hi clean aur proper condition mein chhoda hai jaisa humein mila tha, aur saare dues bhi clear kar diye hain.\n\nElectricity bill ka breakdown:\nMeter reading: 279 to 296 = 17 units\nPer unit rate: ₹8\nTotal: 17 × 8 = ₹136\nHumne ₹136 ka bill pay kar diya hai.\n\nToh kindly next month ka rent start na karein. Ab aap room kisi naye interested person ko allot kar sakte hain.\n\n\n---\n\nKuch feedback dena chahenge, jo future mein PG ke liye helpful ho sakta hai:\n\n1. Friends ko PG mein aane ki permission honi chahiye.\n\n\n2. Thoda loud mein baat ya masti allowed honi chahiye, jab tak disturbance nahi ho.\n\n\n3. Electricity aur Wi-Fi 24×7 available rehna chahiye.\n\n\n4. Water cooler mein current aa raha tha — please check karwa lijiye, thoda unsafe tha.\n\n\n5. Kuch neighbours humein dressing sense ke basis par judge karte the, jo thoda uncomfortable feel hua.\n\n\n6. AC install ho jaaye toh summer mein kaafi better comfort milega.\n\n\n\nHope aap is feedback ko positively lenge. Thank you for your support during our stay 🙏\n\n- Kartik & Keshav",
